utton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2533456\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 13, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104woy1665702925082.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/woy1665702925082.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/woy1665702925082.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"woy1665702925082\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Define Workers\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A worker is a Tomcat process that accepts work from the web server. You need to create a <span class=\"ph filepath\">workers.properties</span> file that defines the workers.\n </p>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"woy1665702925082__li_d23237e1_d23238e1_d23239e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">For the Apache Web Server, create the <span class=\"ph filepath\">worker.properties</span> file in the <span class=\"ph filepath\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ApacheInstallDirectory</var>/Apache/conf</span> directory.\n </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"woy1665702925082__li_d23240e1_d23241e1_d23242e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">For Microsoft IIS, create the <span class=\"ph filepath\">worker.properties</span> file in the Tomcat installation that is working with IIS Redirector, for example, <span class=\"ph filepath\">/tomcat/conf</span>.\n </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"woy1665702925082__li_d23243e1_d23244e1_d23245e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Define two or more workers in the file. For example:\n </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\"># Simple workers configuration file\n# Check the JK Documentation of Tomcat 4 for more information\n#\nps=/\n# List all workers\nworker.list=tomcat1,tomcat2,loadbalancer\n# Redefining the workers of type ajp13\nworker.tomcat1.port=11009\nworker.tomcat1.host=Tomcat_server1\nworker.tomcat1.type=ajp13\nworker.tomcat1.lbfactor=100\nworker.tomcat2.port=12009\nworker.tomcat2.host=Tomcat_server2\nworker.tomcat2.type=ajp13\nworker.tomcat2.lbfactor=100\n# Specify the size of the open connection cache.\nworker.tomcat1.cachesize\n# Specify the load balance factor when used with\n# a load balancing worker.\nworker.loadbalancer.type=lb\nworker.loadbalancer.balanced_workers=tomcat1,tomcat2\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"woy1665702925082__li_d23246e1_d23247e1_d23248e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">For IIS, generate <span class=\"ph filepath\">uriworkermap.properties</span> to mount Uniface servlet and redirect it to the loadbalancer worker.\n </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\"># Simple uri worker map configuration file\n# Check the JK Documentation of Tomcat 4 for more information\n#\ndefault.worker=loadbalancer\nuniface.worker=loadbalancer\n# Mount the Uniface context\n/uniface/servlet/*.*=$(uniface.worker)\n/uniface/*=$(uniface.worker)\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</li></ol></section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533456\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533456\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Define Workers Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 13, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Define Workers A worker is a Tomcat process that accepts work from the web server. You need to create a workers.properties file that defines the workers. For the Apache Web Server, create the worker.properties file in the ApacheInstallDirectory /Apache/conf directory. For Microsoft IIS, create the worker.properties file in the Tomcat installation that is working with IIS Redirector, for example, /tomcat/conf . Define two or more workers in the file. For example: # Simple workers configuration file # Check the JK Documentation of Tomcat 4 for more information # ps=/ # List all workers worker.list=tomcat1,tomcat2,loadbalancer # Redefining the workers of type ajp13 worker.tomcat1.port=11009 worker.tomcat1.host=Tomcat_server1 worker.tomcat1.type=ajp13 worker.tomcat1.lbfactor=100 worker.tomcat2.port=12009 worker.tomcat2.host=Tomcat_server2 worker.tomcat2.type=ajp13 worker.tomcat2.lbfactor=100 # Specify the size of the open connection cache. worker.tomcat1.cachesize # Specify the load balance factor when used with # a load balancing worker. worker.loadbalancer.type=lb worker.loadbalancer.balanced_workers=tomcat1,tomcat2 Copy For IIS, generate uriworkermap.properties to mount Uniface servlet and redirect it to the loadbalancer worker. # Simple uri worker map configuration file # Check the JK Documentation of Tomcat 4 for more information # default.worker=loadbalancer uniface.worker=loadbalancer # Mount the Uniface context /uniface/servlet/*.*=$(uniface.worker) /uniface/*=$(uniface.worker) Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}